=== Server Running ===
vLLM is serving on localhost:8000 on compute node ins086
From the login node, open an SSH tunnel:
  ssh -N -L 8000:localhost:8000 ins086

Then, in a second terminal on the login node, run:
  bash scripts/test_inference.sh localhost 8000 models/Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct

Server will run until the SLURM time limit of (unknown) is hit. Ctrl+C or scancel 8610115 to stop.
